%I+- Increment - Add 1 to DTC Hold Count
+
+ This option adds to the DTC Hold Count for a particular transaction in
+ DTC network. You may use this command when it is necessary to adjust t
+ Hold Count for a transaction that you have already submitted.
+
%D+- Decrement - Subtract 1 from DTC Hold Count
+
+ Use this option to perform the opposite of the%I+ option. If the DTC H
+ Count is decremented to zero, the transaction will be released to run.
+
)PROC
 &ZUP = RBDT0000
)END
